#######################
sphinxcontrib.testbuild
#######################

Test builds of Sphinx-based documentations, using Python.

This projects allows integration of Sphinx documentation builds in continuous
integration platforms, so that you make sure documentation is ok.

For a live demo, see project's continuous integration reports at
https://travis-ci.org/benoitbryon/sphinxcontrib-testbuild


